<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="sk">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>kuklinc-server-2026</title>

<style>
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
}

body{
font-family:Arial, sans-serif;
background:#0c1a0c;
color:white;
}

.main{
height:100vh;
display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
text-align:center;
background:linear-gradient(140deg,#0c1a0c,#133813);
}

h1{
font-size:60px;
color:#35ff7a;
text-shadow:0 0 20px #35ff7a;
}

p{
margin-top:15px;
font-size:18px;
opacity:0.8;
}

.ip{
margin-top:30px;
padding:15px 35px;
border:2px solid #35ff7a;
border-radius:10px;
font-weight:bold;
background:rgba(53,255,122,0.1);
}

.section{
padding:60px 20px;
text-align:center;
}

.boxes{
display:flex;
flex-wrap:wrap;
justify-content:center;
gap:20px;
margin-top:30px;
}

.box{
background:#122412;
padding:25px;
width:250px;
border-radius:12px;
transition:0.3s;
}

.box:hover{
transform:translateY(-5px);
box-shadow:0 0 15px rgba(53,255,122,0.4);
}

footer{
padding:20px;
text-align:center;
background:#050805;
font-size:14px;
opacity:0.6;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="main">
<h1>KUKLINC SERVER</h1>
<p>Moderný Minecraft Survival zážitok</p>
<div class="ip">mc.kuklincserver.online</div>
</div>

<div class="section">
<h2>Prečo sa pripojiť?</h2>
<div class="boxes">
<div class="box">
<h3>Stabilita</h3>
<p>Minimálny lag a rýchly hosting.</p>
</div>
<div class="box">
<h3>Eventy</h3>
<p>Turnaje a špeciálne odmeny.</p>
</div>
<div class="box">
<h3>Komunita</h3>
<p>Aktívni hráči a priateľská atmosféra.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<footer>
© 2026 kuklinc-server-2026
</footer>

</body>
</html>

